article.description: — Tremell Murphy posted 18 points and seven rebounds as Drake edged past Richmond 73-70 on Saturday.
article.headline: Murphy scores 18 to lead Drake over Richmond 73-70
article.linkText: Murphy scores 18 to lead Drake over Richmond 73-70
article.story: DES MOINES, Iowa -- — Tremell Murphy posted 18 points and seven rebounds as Drake edged past Richmond 73-70 on Saturday. A basket by Murphy with 3:36 to go gave Drake the lead and the Bulldogs held on from there. Roman Penn had 12 points for Drake (3-0). Tucker DeVries added 11 points. D.J. Wilkins had 10 points. Tyler Burton scored a career-high 30 points and had nine rebounds for the Spiders (2-2). Grant Golden added 17 points and five assists. Isaiah Wilson had six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
